{
  "stem": "2684.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And God wasn't with me that time because I developed a boil on my side, a huge boil, which had to be cut.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they took me into the emergency room of the factory, and they cut the boil, and I couldn't work.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I, I went back to the hangar, and I just hanged around.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And because I didn't do anything, there was another, what we call, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[GERMAN] is a sicky, like a sicky, in German called [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the reason I know the name because they took us from there to a [GERMAN] lager.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The [GERMAN] lager is a sicky lager where all you had to do was dying.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You hardly had anything to eat, but you didn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's what I was scared of.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And because of my boil, they put us on a truck about-- again, 40 or 50 of us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And not far away from Ausberg, it took about half a day by car, or maybe a day.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we arrived to a lager, a set of lagers, which called Kaufering.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in my days in Kaufbeuren, I heard about Kaufering because people who worked there with me-- who were Fluechtling with me-- they were from a lot of other lagers, not just from Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were in Kaufering.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they said it was a fantastic lager.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You could get potato there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You could go out to the field to get potatoes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You had warmers on which you can bake the potato because that was surviving time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I mean, you didn't talk about clothes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You talked about food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Food was surviving or not.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Even work didn't matter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was no matter what you do as long as you get something to eat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went to Kaufering.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
